title: Big Time Cancellation
description:
Wendi Nix, Joey Galloway, and Greg McElroy react to all of the action in Week 14 as well as a big cancelation in the Big 10. A new head coach is announced in Columbia, and Greg and Joey gives us their College Football Playoff rankings. Jamey Chadwell joins the show.
